Disable swaylock and update swayidle configuration to use system suspend command

This commit disables swaylock to allow system-level suspend hooks to function properly, and modifies the swayidle configuration to suspend the system after 5 minutes of inactivity. This change enhances the integration with greetd and streamlines the user experience on resume.
